rComments: This class is very hard. Took it last semester; there's a lot of work and tons of reading. Tests and quizzes are hard. Wouldn't recommend for a b.s. easy elective

Not too hard of a class, but the exams are pretty difficult.  The tests ask super specific questions, as if he expects you to cheat since it's an online class.  That being said it doesn't take much effort to earn a B but an A will have to be earned.
